Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:30.23,staff2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯:深曉遊人 Black 校對:深曉遊人 Black 時間軸:錄音 後期:電子騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:31.49,tittle,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「竹燈的約定」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備順利的進行著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待晚上 是吧 小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 薰碳 在幹嘛呢 去保幌了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:03:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 再過一會兒就來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好…了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐做到一半扔給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見 晴天娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起大小什麼的 臉啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是祈禱「晴天吧」的方法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 不管怎麼看都是臨終的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的薰碳也完全是正在殺人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不否定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對小啪來說是久違的憧憬之街
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著絕對希望它放晴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就說那麼就做一個晴天娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:03:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸來過之後的第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我說 我們也來做晴天娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我覺得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我去找布料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小啪今天是第三次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是之前的不太記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢 不知怎的記憶模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為困了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為白天和姐姐滑草啦探險啦 玩了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來 小啪睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 而且前一天太期待了睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪碳的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上收拾行李時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了小啪失望的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那個時候和爸爸約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次來的時候 一起看最美的憧憬之街
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那之後爸爸一直很忙沒能帶我來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有實現的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 為了報仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要讓小啪在憧憬之街玩得開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 想給你看最棒的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 昨晚好好睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 完全沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 可以去一下館主那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 有沒有推薦的地方啊 適合告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 墓地怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓地？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫著好可怕啊 緊緊的抱著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的話一次就OK了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墳墓也會亮燈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是黑暗的地方不是也很浪漫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 不來這裏不也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 迷茫地被擁抱 親吻 也很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 要去告白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 乃理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是趁著亮燈而氣氛高漲的時候告白的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然告白還是要女生來做呢 嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道結果會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該走了 要到碰頭的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOOD LUCK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們也去保幌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 小啪的事做完了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 換膠卷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞到蠟燭點燃的味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音碳通過聲音 薰碳通過味道來感受祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃理惠從剛才開始就用肚子感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪碳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動了的話 會糊掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一起在動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望 能停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 可能還是能拍到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用三腳架會比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志保美小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有另一個後備的 這個你用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說起來 是私事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說憧憬之街非常漂亮 就來看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的亮燈開始之前 去吃大阪燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在正要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真開心 剛好肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推薦保幌燒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼堂鄉會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要直呼老師的名字 紅葉饅最好還是白餡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 拜託你下醬油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就有空位置吃馬鈴薯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的土笑話更糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:10:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 到了晚上真的很漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天帶你去兔子島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於 實現約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 就覺得你一定會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 送了謝禮沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下一次把那傢伙也帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都帶著笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰 每個人都帶著不同的心願 來到這個祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家今天都能有美好的回憶就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們 對你們這些未婚的有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用未婚這個詞很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對保幌小姐來個愛的 告白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別吵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪兒來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這可是個好地方 玩的盡興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 你們邀請她去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就做領頭人跟去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後到了好時機你們全都給我走散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始自己去邀請不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我做得到的話還會拜託你們這些人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 嘴滑了 是您們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要牽連進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝謝謝謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對堂鄉老師來說 今天是特別的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個戰略的成功可是擔負在你們肩上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會用短信打暗號的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後3分鐘之內趕過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要遲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙說有什麼人生的問題要請教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天對這個小鎮來說 是特別的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家都有笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:12:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 停 停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明姐姐連防雨的魔法也用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒和祈雨的詛咒搞錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打聽下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的雨沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒問題 雖然也想這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說暫時先等到5點看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還不停的話 就很遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊 我們也做了晴天娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會輸給佐代美姐的詛咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她沒有詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 今天不下也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 小薰 我沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使今年不行 來年還能看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家去寫許願燈籠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟著去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪你要寫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 希望停雨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像小啪會寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以寫些更大的事情噢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 雨不停的話這個也掛不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我果然希望香碳會成為我家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心術不正 心術不正
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昌子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不見 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多久沒見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看看多年不見的憧憬之街而回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為下雨現在超受打擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 難道 你是小啪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我是澤渡楓 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許小啪不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前曾經一起玩過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣野昌子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪是這個春天搬來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昌子現在在東京嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又搬了 現在在橫須賀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 橫須賀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是叫衣笠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我以前住汐入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常去不入斗公園的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也經常去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劍道場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道千石阪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.76,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ちこく阪：橫須賀的一條坡道 漢字寫成千石阪 連接汐入、阪本和不入斗地區）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家就在那附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這啥啊 自言自語的老家talk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會搬來這裏 果然是因為你父親的緣故嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是很有趣的父親 所以我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小孩一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是昌子搬家後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不難過了才搬來這鎮上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨能停就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個小鎮點起光來的話 即使在天國也一定能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 在燈籠上寫上願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能傳遞給在天國的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這樣認為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得這樣 我也在燈籠上寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我在那邊寫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:16:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經4點了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺小鎮的人少了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是客滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面剛空出來了 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為店裏暫時不會忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 香碳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大家 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香碳 等下一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 什…喂 早熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦 會給別的客人添麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做跟蹤狂麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出你真正的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是要等時機…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要告白麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不會讓你妨礙我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更喜歡小香的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是男孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓嬸嬸做你女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你在說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局勢果然是要由女生告白 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪 睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說了昨晚沒睡著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這是小啪回來後第一次的憧憬之街
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是對小啪來說 還是對我來說 都是特別的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是什麼呢 很溫暖的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小薰的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這年還是沒看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這年因為有爸爸在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多想傳達的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的事也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我又開始拍照了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了這裏 交了新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的事物 重要的事物增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不哭也能好起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了5點了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 漂亮啊 漂亮啊 漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈籠也掛上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪的是給父親的信息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是志保美小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:34.55,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(407,566)}遇上更多更多未知事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相機畫得真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:41.76,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起度過的時間都是寶物 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 旁邊的 難道是昌子的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是堂鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 3分鐘內要過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天提早關門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:22:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要向幫忙的老師你道謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長去看祭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼老師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為謝禮的五層大阪燒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大 阪 燒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看到大家的笑容而努力為我們準備的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待我們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.86,0:22:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待這一天的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著令人懷念的回憶的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:22:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種人的回憶重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能看到和以往不同的 這個小鎮特別的面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.56,0:23:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是托小薰和大家的福 今天成為了特別的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.07,0:23:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸的約定好像實現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.43,0:24:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 玉響~hitotose~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.37,0:24:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不變之人改變之時」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:52.22,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜かに遠ざかる雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:21:04.27,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと この道照らしてくれる 星たち
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:14.05,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數えきれない輝き 鏤めて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:21.00,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢へと續く道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:27.76,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星空の下　步いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:37.12,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いくつもの未來を 一緒に話したね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:39.70,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜明けまで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:48.71,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩手に　集めた想い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:58.25,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今は小さく賴りないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.83,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:10.19,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんなの心 笑顏に變えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:17.22,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうすればいいかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:28.91,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳閉じればそっと浮かぶ あなたの面影が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:35.81,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やさしく微笑んだ氣がしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:40.78,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見守っていてね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:13.52,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢の扉を開けたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:18.20,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣持ちの向くままに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.31,0:23:22.90,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠回りもいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:30.30,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷ったら　地圖を廣げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:37.21,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星空の下　步いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:46.51,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつかは私たち 大人になるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:53.36,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂しくてはしゃいでた日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:24:03.96,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとずっと　續きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:52.22,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜靜遠去的雨點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:21:04.27,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄照亮道路的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:14.05,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數的光輝點綴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:21.00,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向夢想延伸的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:27.76,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行走於星空下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:37.12,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起訴說了很多的未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:39.70,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:48.71,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中在雙手的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:58.25,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在還很小很不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.83,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:10.19,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想將大家的心變為笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:17.22,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:28.91,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉起雙瞳後悄悄浮現的你的面龐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:35.81,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種溫柔地微笑著的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:40.78,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一直守護我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:13.52,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打開了夢想的門扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:18.20,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就隨意走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.31,0:23:22.90,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞遠路也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:30.30,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的話 就打開地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:37.21,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行走於星空下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:46.51,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何時我們會變成大人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:53.36,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快樂地歡鬧過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:24:03.96,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能一直延續下去
